<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    There is one vague sex scene, some suggestive dialogue, and a rumor about oral sex. There were no LGBTQ+ characters but there was a magazine given to <a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    There is one vague sex scene, some suggestive dialogue, and a rumor about oral sex. There were no LGBTQ+ characters but there was a magazine given to a character at the end, and lesbian erotica was specified when describing said magazine. <a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
