<div id="review_3068460352" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3068460352" />
    <a title="MissBecka Gee" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/5997380-missbecka-gee"><img alt="MissBecka Gee" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1544171422p2/5997380.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3068460352?book_show_action=true">Jul 17, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="MissBecka Gee" class="user" itemprop="url" name="MissBecka Gee" href="/user/show/5997380-missbecka-gee">MissBecka Gee</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5997380-missbecka-gee?shelf=z2020-books-i-read">z2020-books-i-read</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5997380-missbecka-gee?shelf=netgalley-books-read">netgalley-books-read</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5997380-missbecka-gee?shelf=kindle-already-done">kindle-already-done</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3068460352" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4526895452347167103">I had a blast getting trapped in 1991 with Cassie and Drea!<br/>Fantastic characters in a cute story with so much nostalgia (both good &amp; bad lol).<br/>Thanks to NetGalley and St. Martin&apos;s Press for my DRC.<br/><br/>&quot;The chlorinated waters of the Wishing Well ran black with mascara today.&quot;</span>
  <span id="freeText4526895452347167103" style="display:none">I had a blast getting trapped in 1991 with Cassie and Drea!<br />Fantastic characters in a cute story with so much nostalgia (both good &amp; bad lol).<br />Thanks to NetGalley and St. Martin's Press for my DRC.<br /><br />"The chlorinated waters of the Wishing Well ran black with mascara today."</span>
